reviewText: Oh the memories of delightfull programs of Mr. Dressup! Purchasing this for a new granddaughter, she will definitely enjoy watching it!
Great show for children to watch. It is educational, encourages them to use their imagination, plus is totally clean. .
5 star rating, this is a great DVD filled with lots of educational tools for learning, it is fun and interactive, I would love to order more Mr. Dress up videos.
REMINDS ME OF OUR KIDS WATCHING IT WHEN THEY WERE YOUNG, PROGRAM CAME IN FROM CANADA IN WINDSOR EVERY MORNING
